<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>难忘的集体生日会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/a385c34b765f4ca8b92055d08f0607e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
